      <title>亨特对英国 ISA 提振英国股市的想法“非常感兴趣”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/jeremy-hunt-very-attracted-by-british-isa-to-boost-uk-stocks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国财政大臣杰里米·亨特表示，他对创建一个投资英国股票的免税储蓄账户的想法“非常感兴趣”——所谓的英国 ISA –作为提振英国陷入困境的股市努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/jeremy-hunt-very-attracted-by-british-isa-to-boost-uk-stocks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 22:11:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cielo 股东将在收购要约中寻求更高价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/cielo-shareholders-said-to-seek-higher-price-in-buyout-offer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，巴西两家最大的银行计划将支付公司 Cielo SA 私有化，但该计划遭到少数利益相关者的反对，这些利益相关者正计划通过谈判获得更高的价格。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-08/cielo-shareholders-said-to-seek-higher-price-in-buyout-offer</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Feb 2024 22:04:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
